# Ingenius - AI Agent Operations Command Centre for ugenie.ai

## Project Context
Mission-critical internal dashboard for operational efficiency. Every feature must reduce manual work and improve workflow for the founding team.

## Tech Stack
Next.js 14+ (App Router), TypeScript (strict), Tailwind CSS, npm

## Code Standards
- TypeScript strict mode (no `any` types)
- Functional components with hooks
- PascalCase for components, kebab-case for files
- Conventional commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, etc.)
- Error handling and loading states required

## File Structure  
- `src/app/` - App Router pages
- `src/components/` - Reusable components
- `src/lib/` - Utilities
- `src/types/` - TypeScript definitions

## UI Principles
- Professional enterprise dashboard design
- Real-time data visualization priority
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Clear visual hierarchy and feedback
- Accessibility compliance

## Key Focus Areas
1. Operational efficiency optimization
2. Clean, maintainable, self-documenting code  
3. Proper error handling and edge cases
4. Performance and scalability
5. Security for sensitive operational data

See `.cursor/rules.md` for detailed guidelines. 